I. Prepare

    1) Place content of that directory in your DocumentRoot, for example in "d:\tools\apache\htdocs\prototype"
    2) Download Dojo Toolkit source code http://download.dojotoolkit.org/release-1.8.0/dojo-release-1.8.0-src.zip
    3) Unpack the archive to "d:\tools\apache\htdocs\prototype\source". This directory shuld contain:

            dijit
            dojo
            dojox
            nhs
            utils

    4) Open the test page (test_prototype.html) in your browser.

            http://localhost/prototype/nhs/tests/test_prototype.html

II. Minify

    1) Open comand line prompt and change current directory to d:\tools\apache\htdocs\prototype
    2) Run ant script by executing command:

            "ant" or "ant minify"

       This will take about 3 minutes to complete. Additional directory called
       "build" should be created in "d:\tools\apache\htdocs\prototype\source"
    3) Open the test page (test_prototype_build.html) in your browser

            http://localhost/prototype/nhs/tests/test_prototype_build.html
